units metal
atom_style atomic
boundary p  p  p

read_data pristine.in

pair_style ?pair_style?
pair_coeff * * ?potential? ?elements?

neighbor ?skin? bin
neigh_modify delay 0 check yes

dump 1 all custom 1 relax.dump id type x y z

log pristine.log
thermo_style custom step pe press vol
thermo 1

fix 1 all box/relax iso 0.0
min_style cg
minimize 1.0e-10 1.0e-10 1000 10000

delete_atoms group all
read_data defective.in add merge

log defective.log

unfix 1
minimize 1.0e-10 1.0e-10 1000 10000